      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Ocean Dream Samudra at Ancol"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Ocean Dream Samudra is the largest oceanarium unit consisting of dolphin performances, sea lion performances, various animal performances, animal demonstrations, marine and freshwater fish aquariums and gardens which are the habitat of various kinds of birds."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Get to know and learn more about a variety of water animals at Ocean Dream Samudra."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "One of the biggest oceanarium in Indonesia."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Meet cute little penguin and more water animals, only at Ocean Dream Samudra."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "There are a variety of rides and attractions at Ocean Dream Samudra Ancol. Below are some of the highlights."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Mola Mola: The rides are definitely really fun and make you happy at Ocean Dream Samudra, our adrenaline is pumped up, we are invited to get dizzy together until we spin 360 degrees while feeling the rides go up and down. Enjoy it while laughing with your family because you can sit facing each other. At first, you might be nervous, but I guarantee that one time won't be enough, you'll definitely want to ride the rides many times. Another excitement is that we can recharge again after a day of watching the show at Ocean Dream Samudra."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Penguin Palace: Humboldt penguins from South America usually nest on rocky beaches. You can witness the behaviour of 11 cute and adorable Humboldt penguins at the Penguin Palace exhibit. You can also interact to feed them. Humboldt penguins like to eat anchovies, small sardines and squid."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Carousel: This is Ocean Dream Samudra's new ride. This carousel is presented with cute animal shapes such as sea horses, shells, dolphins, and ostrich. It's really exciting to be able to enjoy the rides and capture warm moments with the family."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Operation Hours: Please kindly visit Ocean Dream Samudra Ancol official website for any updates of operation hours."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restrictions: Please kindly visit Ocean Dream Samudra Ancol official website for rides & attractions' height restrictions."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
